				<h2>Good Morning! Here are your To-Dos today</h2>
				<p>The first page after logging in, the Dashboard shows you your most urgent tasks for the day and gives you a preview of what’s ahead. All the ways a surgeon or lab member would want to slice or dice their list of open cases, the Dashboard has a shortcut for it.</p>

