				<h2>FINDING ONE CASE OUT OF HUNDREDS</h2>
				<p>The goal of Cases is for users to find the specific case memo they needed at a high level. I focus on users filtering by status or timing, sorting the results, and viewing the results either as cards or a list.</p>
